Privacy Policy for Igbo Calendar

Effective Date: September 4th, 2023

Introduction
Welcome to Igbo Calendar ("the App"). This Privacy Policy is meant to help you understand how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our calendar application. We take your privacy seriously and are committed to protecting any data you may provide.

Information We Do Not Collect

1. Personal Information: We do not collect, store, or request any personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, or any other personally identifiable information.
2. Location Information: We do not collect your location data or track your physical whereabouts.
3. Device Information: We do not access or gather information about your device, including but not limited to device type, operating system, or unique device identifiers.

Usage Information
Our Igbo Calendar application is designed to provide information about market days in Igbo land only. It does not track or store any user data or interactions within the app.

Children's Privacy
Our Igbo Calendar application is suitable for use by children. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. If you believe that we may have collected personal information from a child under 13, please contact us at [gabrieoranekwu@gmail.com](mailto:gabrieoranekwu@gmail.com) so that we can delete such information.

Third-Party Services
We do not integrate or use any third-party services that may collect your data while you use our Igbo Calendar application.

Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. The most current version of the Privacy Policy will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or the way your data is handled in our Igbo Calendar application, please contact us at [gabrieoranekwu@gmail.com](mailto:gabrieoranekwu@gmail.com).

Thank you for using Igbo Calendar!
